<Author>Miriam08
<Content>Nice, area is very quiet Hotel is nice, maybe not quiet 4 star but good value for money. rooms are very clean, comfortable and not too small. Breakfast is probably not worth it - nicer cafes around. Location great for Ku'dam, although that is now a much quiter area than the main parts of Berlin. For going out to sightseeing and in the evenings you have to take a S-bahn, station is about 10min walk from hotel ,jouney to most places of interest take around 15/20 min but trains run all night and the excellent 7 day travel tickets make it very simple. 
