<Content>Staff is forgetful, but good location We booked two rooms far in advance. One week before our arrival we again called the hotel and again recommended them to get a nice room for my grandma as this trip was going to be her birthday present. However, after arrival my grandma got a smoking room, smelling disgustingly. Maybe, some people don't bother, we do! I reminded the staff about my inquiry but they were not able (nor willing) to remember. Poor for a family-run business in my eyes. Beside this the rooms were clean and the location just by the Kurf眉rstendamm is unique. After all, I wouldn't go back to this hotel as the staff was not that friendly one could expect it to be in a family-run hotel. 
